data.product_title: Naruto: Shippuden Gaara of the Sand Limited Edition Ultimate Diorama Statue
data.product_description: Someday, I want to feel needed by someone. Not as a frightening weapon... but as the Kazekage of the Hidden Sand Village. HEX Collectibles presents the Gaara Ultimate Diorama Statue in 1:8 scale from Naruto Shippuden. The statue measures 24.4 inches tall, inspired by the battle scene between Gaara and Deidara. As the Fifth Kazekage, Gaara fights with Deidara while protecting the village from being involved.A huge gourd tied on the back, Gaara wears a long-sleeved crimson robe standing firmly on the sand and stones. The Fifth Kazekage stares at his enemy with a stern look, and manipulates the sand rushing out of the base and his gourd, which adds a powerful feeling to the statue.Behind Gaara, the One-Tailed Shukaku waves its sharp claws and howls angrily to the sky. This monstrous Tanuki is fully sculpted in the likeness of its anime appearance, with realistic gravel textures and black cursed seal markings all over its massive sand-brown body and tail. The fluid design as well as dusts made by the One-Tailed Shukaku complement and epitomize a nervous a nervous but exciting battle scene for collectors.Naruto Shippuden fans, don't miss your chance to add this Gaara statue to your UDS collection!
